1.10
log
@So long, rdconfig. You won't be missed.

ok matthew@@
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: rdconfig.8,v 1.9 2007/05/31 19:20:28 jmc Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: rdconfig.8,v 1.1.1.1 1995/10/08 22:40:41 gwr Exp $
